skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: memory power
des:
This is a game which tests your memory capacity. You are required to remember the list of words in the same sequence as mentioned by Alexa. Alexa will subsequently asks five questions for which you should provide answers from your memory. Alexa will calculate your score depending on the answers.
Special thanks to github for providing the list of words and the api provider dictionaryapi.dev
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
